      interface  ObservableSUL<S,​I,​O>

      interface  StateLocalInputSUL<I,​O>
      A System Under Learning (SUL) which can additionally report the inputs that the SUL can process in its current state, i.e. inputs that will not trigger a SULException when used in the next invocation of the step(Object) method return an otherwise "undefined" behavior.
